Collection of Information:
  When you use ChaPy, we do not collect any personally identifiable information unless explicitly provided by you.
  We may collect anonymous usage data such as engagement time, browser type and other analytics to improve our service.

Data Storage:
  All messages sent through ChaPy are stored in a decentralized manner without any central authority having access to them.
  It is essential for users to understand that they have sole responsibility for managing their own decentralized data storage systems and implementing appropriate security measures.

Third-Party Services:
  We do not share your personal information with third-party services except when required by law or as necessary for system maintenance or security purposes.
  However, please note that external links shared within the application may take you outside of our control and privacy policy.

Security Measures:
  We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure.
  Despite these efforts, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure; therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Children's Privacy:
  ChaPy is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal information from individuals under the age of 13 without parental consent.

Changes to this Policy:
  Please note that this Privacy Policy may be subject to change at any time without prior notice. Any modifications will be effective immediately upon posting on our website.

Contact Information:
  If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the use of your personal information, please contact us at mr.sairexer@gmail.com.
